     C                   MOVEL     'MIDAS  '     W0MSGF
     C                   EXSR      SRERR
     C                   ENDIF
     C*
     C**  If the currency has been retrieved earlier, position the
     C**  Currency Data data structure on the relevant occurrence.
     C*
     C                   ELSE
     C     C             OCCUR     SDCURR
     C                   ENDIF
